latestPosts.caption:
DIL-LUMINATI INDIA TOUR- DELHI DAY 1
The UNFATHOMABLE has happened!!! We performed with @diljitdosanjh ahhh I’m screamingggg!!!😩😩😩
Punjabi aa gaye oyeeee!!🧨✨🧨

A glance of Diljit paaji is enough to make your day. I will never forget rehearsing in his presence and on top of it, I got to be his🪽angel🪽!!! Opening the show for paaji and handing him over his mic, I can’t believe that was ME???😭😭😭 The humblest and sweetest, sir greets everyone with a smile on his face and Sat Shri Akaal🙏

This was not on my 2024 vision board🧿🪬All because of our main man @isshehzaankhan ❤️❤️❤️
Love you more than you know. Can’t thank you enough for this opportunity. Words fall short to describe your talent, hard work and professionalism. But on top of all that, there’s so much more to learn from you as a human being, the person that you are. No one like you💌🫶💌

Major shoutout to my girls performing with me!! We go up, we go together💟💟💟
